OL,3,CPolice investigate after man dies in
OL,4,CWolverhampton house fire
OL,6,FA man in his 70s has died and four
OL,7,Fothers have been hospitalised after
OL,8,Ftwo house fires in the Bilston area of
OL,9,FWolverhampton.
OL,11,FA cordon is in place on Lunt Place and
OL,12,FMarbury Drive while police and fire
OL,13,Fservices jointly investigate the fires.
OL,15,FWest Midlands Police has confirmed is
OL,16,Ftreating the two fires as being
OL,17,Fconnected.
