OL,3,CPolice investigate after man dies in
OL,4,CWolverhampton house fire
OL,6,FWest Midlands Fire Service said it was
OL,7,Ffirst called at 2:19am on Saturday to
OL,8,Fa house fire in Lunt Place, and led
OL,9,Fthree people inside the house to
OL,10,Fsafety.
OL,12,FThey, along with a fourth person who
OL,13,Fwas outside, were taken to hospital
OL,14,Fwith injuries which are not believed
OL,15,Fto be life-threatening.
OL,17,FFire crews were then called at 2:30am
OL,18,Fto a second house fire on an adjoining
OL,19,Froad, Marbury Drive, where a man in
OL,20,Fhis 70s died at the scene.
