OL,3,CPolice investigate after man dies in
OL,4,CWolverhampton house fire
OL,6,FWest Midlands Fire Service said the
OL,7,Ffire "involved a detached, two-storey
OL,8,Fhouse, with fire affecting virtually
OL,9,Fall of the property."
OL,11,FIt added: "Our crews worked in
OL,12,Fchallenging conditions to contain and
OL,13,Fextinguish the fire.
OL,15,F"Sadly, a man believed to be in his
OL,16,Fseventies was confirmed to have died
OL,17,Fat the scene.
OL,19,F"Our thoughts are with everyone
OL,20,Faffected by these events."
